    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="945473939">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-945473939" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-945473939" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="945473939">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/whitesailor/">carrie柔光</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-09-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">以八道湾十一号为轴心将三兄弟的命运并置一处，简直看得有些触目惊心了。与大哥三弟相比，周作人实在不是入世之人，可怜见“苦雨、苦茶、苦住、苦药”都苦不及“寿则多辱”。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="993892798">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-993892798" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-993892798" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="993892798">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/pandatou/">龢青</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-12-31</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">文中动容者多处。兄弟如何倪墙，鲁迅圣母无报，二先生寿则多辱，三先生抛妻弃子，周氏三兄弟的结局天上地下迥异非常。回看短暂的八道湾的友爱和乐的时光，心酸不止。最后看到周丰二手绘八道湾地图莫名戳泪点。图上清晰地表明鲁迅亲自摘得松树和其它各种植被的准确方位可知就算几十年过去了世事辗转变化，丰二对儿时八道湾的情景和人情依旧难以忘怀。八道湾承载的感情纠葛、文艺学术、政治变换等等，容量难以估量。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="945884710">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
